      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Shaman&amp;message.id=5533#M5533</link>
      <description>This used to be quite an art; however, since the contextual popup menus you get when right-clicking on an empty spell gem, it is really a waste of time. Once you have saved your several (up to 10) spell sets, just use /mem main or whatever to load your spells. See also &lt;a target="_blank" href="http://samanna.net/sham.info/tips.shtml"&gt;Samanna.net&lt;/a&gt; for spell set advice.</description>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Jan 2006 13:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
