    <item>
      <title>Re: Spellbook layout</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Shaman&amp;message.id=5669#M5669</link>
      <description>So, how do I set up such spell sets?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Mem the spells you want to use for buffing.&lt;br&gt;Right-click spellbook icon (what you left-click to bring up the actual spellbook) and you should get options like save/load/delete spellset.&lt;br&gt;Select save and give it a name, like &amp;quot;buffs&amp;quot;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Repeat for other sets, like solo, travel, whatever.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;See also &lt;a href="http://samanna.net/sham.info/tips.shtml" target="_blank"&gt;Samanna.net&lt;/a&gt; for spell set advice.</description>
